Crebain gather upon Cracabor, the highest hill near Twickenburg. These fell birds give unease to the warriors stationed nearby.
The hill of Cracabor is the highest point in the Wold and is located just north of Twickenburg.
Return to Tidlac, Sergeant of Twickenburg
Sergeant Tidlac is keeping watch on the road from the fort of Twickenburg, between Harwick and Floodwend.
